snippet.title: Sonic 1 Pilot - CGS 2021
snippet.description:
Sonic 1 pilot asks what if the original sonic’s concepts never changed... Explore Sonic 1 in a new, pretty crazy way!

This game is sadly not playable at our event this year, but make sure to keep an eye on it!
